  ;; --- COMPONENT PLACEMENT & WIRING NOTES ---
  (text "=== LOWER PCB  rev 2.0  ===\n\n*** XIAO ESP32-S3 handles: LiPo charging, USB ESD, battery ADC internally ***\n*** Removed: U2 TP4056, U4 USBLC6, R5/R6 voltage divider, LED1/LED2 ***\n\nU1: Seeed XIAO ESP32-S3 (castellated module)\n     PLACEMENT: North half of board, USB-C end facing north/forward\n     GPIO1  -> JOY_X\n     GPIO2  -> JOY_Y\n     GPIO3  -> JOY_SW\n     GPIO9  -> BT_SYNC (SW_BT, pull-up R_PU_BT)\n     GPIO10 -> ADC_BAT (onboard voltage divider, reads battery level 0-3.3V)\n     GPIO5  -> BTN_LEFT\n     GPIO6  -> BTN_RIGHT\n     GPIO7  -> BTN_BACK\n     GPIO8  -> BTN_FWD\n     3V3    -> 3V3 rail (output)\n     GND    -> GND\n     BAT+   -> BAT+ rail (connects to J2 positive pin + SW1)\n     USB-C  -> handled internally (charge + HID data)\n     KEEPOUT: no copper within 3mm of antenna (module NW corner)\n     NOTE: GPIO10/ADC_BAT has onboard divider already - connect directly\n     NOTE: Onboard charger LED (red) on XIAO module itself\n\nU3: AP2112K-3.3V (SOT-23-5)\n     PLACEMENT: East quadrant\n     VIN  -> switched BAT+ via SW1 (master power)\n     VOUT -> 3V3 rail\n     GND  -> GND\n     CE   -> VIN (always on when SW1 ON)\n     PURPOSE: Powers J4 joystick module and J3 FPC 3V3 line\n     NOTE: XIAO has its own internal 3V3 regulator for its own logic.\n           External U3 provides 3V3 for peripherals (joystick + FPC).\n\nJ1: USB-C receptacle (mid-mount)\n     PLACEMENT: North board edge, USB-C facing forward/north\n     VBUS -> XIAO VBUS pad (charging)\n     D+   -> XIAO USB_DP (internal ESD on XIAO)\n     D-   -> XIAO USB_DN\n     GND  -> GND\n     CC1  -> R10(5.1k) -> GND\n     CC2  -> R11(5.1k) -> GND\n\nJ2: JST-PH 2-pin right-angle\n     PLACEMENT: SW quadrant\n     Pin1 -> BAT+ (connects to XIAO BAT pad + SW1 COM + U3 VIN)\n     Pin2 -> GND\n     Battery: 3.7V LiPo 400mAh typical\n\nJ3: FPC 6-pin 0.5mm top-contact\n     PLACEMENT: Center-south (between J4 joystick and south edge)\n     Pin1 -> 3V3\n     Pin2 -> GND\n     Pin3 -> BTN_LEFT  (GPIO5)\n     Pin4 -> BTN_RIGHT (GPIO6)\n     Pin5 -> BTN_BACK  (GPIO7)\n     Pin6 -> BTN_FWD   (GPIO8)\n     NOTE: BTN pull-ups R1-R4 on upper PCB, not here\n\nJ4: Alps RKJXV1224005 (direct THT solder, no module, no header)\n     PLACEMENT: Board center, shaft pointing up through body shell coupler\n     Body: 18.2 x 21.7mm, height 11.2mm, shaft adds ~10mm more\n     10 pins: 4 mounting legs (structural, tie to GND pour) + 6 signal pins\n     X-axis: CCW->3V3, Wiper->JOY_X(GPIO1), CW->GND\n     Y-axis: CCW->3V3, Wiper->JOY_Y(GPIO2), CW->GND\n     SW push: one pin->GND, other->JOY_SW(GPIO3) with R_PU5 10k pull-up to 3V3\n     Pin hole dia: 1.0mm signal pins, 1.5mm mounting legs\n     Datasheet: https://tech.alpsalpine.com/e/products/detail/RKJXV1224005/\n     Buy: https://www.mouser.com/ProductDetail/Alps-Alpine/RKJXV1224005\n     LCSC: C146170\n\nSW1: SPDT slide switch MSK-12C02\n     PLACEMENT: West board edge\n     COM -> BAT+\n     NO  -> U3 VIN (cuts 3V3 to peripherals)\n     NOTE: XIAO continues to charge via USB regardless of SW1 position\n\nSW2: Tactile 3x4mm (BOOT)\n     PLACEMENT: East of U1\n     GPIO0 -> GND when pressed (firmware flash mode with SW3)\n\nSW3: Tactile 3x4mm (RESET)\n     PLACEMENT: East of U1, below SW2\n     EN -> GND when pressed\n\nSW_BT: Tactile 3x4mm (BT SYNC/PAIR)\n     PLACEMENT: South board edge, base_ring cutout at sw_bt_angle=90deg\n     GPIO9 -> GND when pressed\n     Pull-up: R_PU_BT 10k from 3V3 -> GPIO9\n     Firmware: tap=reconnect, hold 3s=BLE pair mode\n\nResistors:\n     R_PU5:   10k 0402  3V3->JOY_SW (GPIO3 pull-up)\n     R_PU_BT: 10k 0402  3V3->GPIO9  (BT sync pull-up)\n     R10:    5.1k 0402  USB-C CC1->GND\n     R11:    5.1k 0402  USB-C CC2->GND\n     REMOVED: R5/R6 (VBAT divider), R7/R8/R9 (TP4056 PROG/LED)\n\nDecoupling caps:\n     C1-C3: 100nF 0402  3V3 rail near U1 and U3\n     C4:    10uF  0805  3V3 bulk\n     C5:    10uF  0805  BAT+ bulk\n     REMOVED: C6 (VBUS bulk - handled by XIAO internally)"
    (at 120 30 0)
    (uuid "00000001-0001-0001-0001-000000000099")
    (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27)) (justify left))
  )
